9defa2e.jpg","text":"\"Books are so much more fun!” says Puchku. \n“Look! You see a circle? And this straight line? Push it in, pull that out, and it becomes a letter. Line up the letters, and you have a word!\nWords can be wise, words can be funny, words can be sad and words can be sunny. \nWhen you put words together, they make sentences. \nAnd sentences become stories. Read it and WHOOSH! \nYou are in another world! ”","words":[[78,"\"Books"],[79,"are"],[80,"so"],[81,"much"],[82,"more"],[83,"fun!”"],[84,"says"],[85,"Puchku."],[86,"“Look!"],[87,"You"],[88,"see"],[89,"a"],[90,"circle?"],[91,"And"],[92,"this"],[93,"straight"],[94,"line?"],[95,"Push"],[96,"it"],[97,"in,"],[98,"pull"],[99,"that"],[100,"out,"],[101,"and"],[102,"it"],[103,"becomes"],[104,"a"],[105,"letter."],[106,"Line"],[107,"up"],[108,"the"],[109,"letters,"],[110,"and"],[111,"you"],[112,"have"],[113,"a"],[114,"word!"],[115,"Words"],[116,"can"],[117,"be"],[118,"wise,"],[119,"words"],[120,"can"],[121,"be"],[122,"funny,"],[123,"words"],[124,"can"],[125,"be"],[126,"sad"],[127,"and"],[128,"words"],[129,"can"],[130,"be"],[131,"sunny."],[132,"When"],[133,"you"],[134,"put"],[135,"words"],[136,"together,"],[137,"they"],[138,"make"],[139,"sentences."],[140,"And"],[141,"sentences"],[142,"become"],[143,"stories."],[144,"Read"],[145,"it"],[146,"and"],[147,"WHOOSH!"],[148,"You"],[149,"are"],[150,"in"],[151,"another"],[152,"world!"],[153,"”"]]},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/53485/size6/04fa79c47f0b7a7dc00ed301bb764d65.jpg","text":"But today, Puchku is in a fix.\nShe has run out of books to read!\nAll the books that she could reach in the library, \nshe’s read from Chapter One to The End.","words":[[154,"But"],[155,"today,"],[156,"Puchku"],[157,"is"],[158,"in"],[159,"a"],[160,"fix."],[161,"She"],[162,"has"],[163,"run"],[164,"out"],[165,"of"],[166,"books"],[167,"to"],[168,"read!"],[169,"All"],[170,"the"],[171,"books"],[172,"that"],[173,"she"],[174,"could"],[1